miniblog Plugin for DokuWiki

A simple blog plugin that treats pages in 'blog' namespace as blog
entries, based on the following plugins: blog, include, blogtng, disqus.

Configurations:
    specify the disqus shortname in configuration manager

Syntax:
    1. Displaying a list of blog entries
        <miniblog>
    2. Displaying a list of blog entries when using 'twentyfifteen' template
        <miniblog twentyfifteen>
    2. Adding disqus comment to a post
        ~~DISQUS~~

Feed:
    The feed URL is "feed.php?mode=miniblog".

All documentation for this plugin can be found at
https://github.com/lainme/dokuwiki-plugin-miniblog

If you install this plugin manually, make sure it is installed in
lib/plugins/miniblog/ - if the folder is called different it
will not work!

Please refer to http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugins for additional info
on how to install plugins in DokuWiki.

